Observer design pattern is the behavioral design pattern that allows some objects to notify other objects about
changes in their state.

The observer pattern provides a way to subscribe and unsubscribe to and from events for any object
that implements  a subscriber interface.

Observer design pattern

1.Provider(The one who is providing the information to all the subscriber/listener/observer)
2.Listener/observer:who listen the information send from the provider

provider has many subscriber
one to many relationship

Java->EventListener

Website Flipkart
Flipkart[Provider]/Subject-> offers notification to all his subscriber
by default->flipkart sign in
Listener/Observer: Either subscriber/unsubscribe


